 \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will take place at 10.30pm on Wednesday, then 9.30pm every other evening until Saturday 7 September.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremony will be broadcast from 8pm-11pm on Sunday 8 September, immediately followed by the last leg.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The closing ceremony\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"the last leg\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the Games, coverage will start from 8am, with the breakfast show presented by Billy Monger and Vick Hope.\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 2046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2019, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billy_Monger\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Billy Monger\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billy_Monger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billy_Monger\"}, {\"begin\": 2036, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vick_Hope\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vick Hope\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vick_Hope\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vick_Hope\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"coverage\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"the breakfast show\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"JJ Chalmers, one of the faces of the recent Olympics, will then take over for the Daytime Live show from 11am-3pm, before Balding and Rose Ayling-Ellis will helm the afternoon edition.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"JJ Chalmers\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"the faces\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"the recent Olympics\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"the Daytime Live show\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"Balding\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"Rose Ayling-Ellis\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"the afternoon edition\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Balding will then return for the evening show alongside Adepitan and Simmonds, before The Last Leg and a highlights show with Josh Pugh and Gaz Choudhury from 10.30pm end the day's action.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Balding\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening show\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"Adepitan\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"Simmonds\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Leg\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"a highlights\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"Josh Pugh\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"Gaz Choudhury\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"10.30pm end\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"the day's action\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paralympics is a wonderful opportunity to watch some different sports, or fresh takes on classics.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paralympics\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"a wonderful opportunity\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"some different sports\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh takes\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\